ğŸ—‚ Event Types (Cards)
Private Event

Only users explicitly invited by the host can access the event

No shareable link; attendees cannot invite others

Invite-Only Event

Users invited by the host receive a shareable link

Anyone who receives the link can access the event only if they meet the hostâ€™s predefined requirements (e.g., verified account, friend of attendee, location-based, etc.)

Public Event

Open to all users

Shareable public link allows anyone to join or RSVP, even without an account

